osed F-B training\nschemes in 5G radio access are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Feb 2018 19:09:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 22 Sep 2018 18:46:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-25"}
