ized white dwarf is sufficient to power the excess\nelectromagnetic radiation emitted by the binary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Feb 2018 19:38:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Jun 2018 04:11:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2018 19:49:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-19"}
